metadata.name: World of ANNA | The First Insight
metadata.description:
A powerful story discovered through Web 3 â€“ 
Project ANNA (A New Nation) is an animated short series that explores the world of heroes and villains after the war between human and synthetic intelligence. Collectors will be by our side throughout our journey, with the ultimate goal to air on mainstream platforms such as Youtube, Netflix or Disney+.

Project ANNA (MTHRNFT) is a project based in Malaysia.

After the establishment of MTHRNFT on BNB chain, we are now migrating to the ETH chain as we wish to seek wider audience to garner more attention on our project. We are at the stage of propelling Project ANNA towards the end goal by being in development stage and the production of animation shorts based on characters in the series.

This OE is a way for us to commemorate our endeavors to be a powerhouse on  Ethereum chain, and towards the success of our migration

As a token of appreciation, anyone who acquires this OE will be able to burn and redeem a fully developed animation in the near future. Total number of this edition will remain a secret for now but will be less than 10  
 
We thank you in advance for showing support by purchasing, either for the sake of the art or to purely to show support towards our cause, or both

LLA!
